message.body: HIII I think I missed our phone date last night. Or was it supposed to be tonight? I was stuck at work until 10 last night -- it's a nutty week for me! Sunday evening might be better, actually? How does that look for you??

Haiii no worries, I missed it too! My mom called and that basically consumed my entire evening haha...but yes Sunday evening is good for me!! Good luck at work until then, you poor thing! I'll try to send you some amusing entertainment...
Hahaha oh dang! Ok will put it in my calendar for Sunday evening! YAY! Busy with planning a conference for next week but it's ok! Love you!
HOLY CRAP YOU'RE GETTING MARRIED IN 37 DAYS
I mean I knew it was soon but it's just now hitting me. Omg.
Right?!?!?!??! Next Wednesday it will be ONE MONTH!!!
Stop OMG I'm going to cry HAHAHAHAHA
